    },
    {
      "id": "phase3-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 800,
      "y": 400,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "Weeks 5-8 | High Risk\n\n• PayBotEscrow.sol (Solidity)\n• Upgradeable proxy pattern\n• escrow-client.ts (SDK)\n• Escrow states:\n  LOCKED → RELEASED\n  → DISPUTED → RESOLVED\n  → AUTO-RELEASED (timeout)\n• Auto-route tx > $100\n• Arbiter dispute resolution\n• Security audit required\n\nNew: contracts/, escrow-*.ts",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
